Inglese:
Shake Your Style is the app for the stylish people looking for an easy way to manage the wardrobe.
Take snapshots of your best garments and shoes, sort them by type, season or preference and keep them on your device during shopping time. 
Are you buying a garment and do you want to check if it fits well your wardrobe and style? Do you have a similar item but you forgot about it? Grab your device and open "Shake Your Style". Few taps and you will never buy again a garment you already have in your wardrobe.
Shake your device to combine your wardrobe items by the current season and your taste. The app is so easy and funny that you will never stop shaking to discover new matchings.



Please note that the following requirements are needed for the app optional features:
- GPS: if your device is GPS enabled, the app will obtain the current temperature automatically (otherwise you will have to enter it)
- SHAKE: you will be able to sort by shake only on devices with accelerometer
- CAM: you will need a cam to capture your garments, otherwise you will need to import the pictures from the device's photo album.




